definition: to arrange/to line up/file/series/(in data tables) column/(Tw) row

to go out/to come out/to occur/to produce/to go beyond/to rise/to put forth/to happen/(used after a verb to indicate an outward direction or a positive result)/classifier for dramas, plays, operas etc

sentences.english: How many offerings are listed in these first seven chapters?
sentences.chinese: 在利未記的頭七章總共列出了多少種獻祭？

sentences.english: In this dictionary both spelling is show when both is possible.
sentences.chinese: 在兩種拼法皆可時，本詞典將之一併列出。

sentences.english: A listing of all the museums and institutions represented on the HAR web site.
sentences.chinese: 列出所有的博物館和機構派代表參加的Har網站。

sentences.english: All artifacts in the selected repository or project will be listed.
sentences.chinese: 選中儲存庫或者項目中的所有工件都會列出來。

sentences.english: In the table1 arelisted the data obtained.
sentences.chinese: 表1中所列出的是所獲得的數據。

sentences.english: The table below lists some of those methods.
sentences.chinese: 下表列出了其中的一些方法。

sentences.english: She published a book listing 659 names;
sentences.chinese: 她出版的一本書，就列出了659名受害者。

sentences.english: Several different types of locks are available, some of them are listed below.
sentences.chinese: 鎖具有幾種不同的類型，下面列出了其中一些。

sentences.english: Below I listed some best rewarding wow gold farming spots.
sentences.chinese: 下面我列出了一些最有價值的謝文東農業景點。

sentences.english: The name of the field is listed in the first column.
sentences.chinese: 第一列中列出了字段名。

sentences.english: All references given must be referred to in the main body of the thesis.
sentences.chinese: 所以列出的參考文獻必須與論文的主題相關聯。

sentences.english: There will be mulitple competitors prices listed on each of my product pages.
sentences.chinese: 將多張有競爭對手在我的產品的每個網頁列出的價格。

sentences.english: Registered type libraries are listed in Available type libraries .
sentences.chinese: 中會列出已登錄的型別程式庫。

sentences.english: How do I enumerate the display devices in a multi-monitor system?
sentences.chinese: 我如何在多顯示器系統中列出各個顯示設備？

sentences.english: The first seven fields above are used in connecting to the directory server.
sentences.chinese: 上面列出了連接到目錄服務器時所使用的前七個字段。

sentences.english: Here are instructions on how to announce an elopement.
sentences.chinese: 下面我會就怎樣去宣告私奔列出一些建議。

to sum up/to summarize/to conclude from facts/induction (method of deduction in logic)
thorough and detailed/exhaustive/the tedious details in full
summary/to summarize/to collect (data, receipts etc)/to gather and report
to contrast/to compare/to place side by side for comparison (as parallel texts)/to check
